<h1>Your feedback is important to us.</h1>
<div class="row">
	<div class="span12">
		<p>This whole event was created for /v/, by /v/. We want to know what you thought about it, so that if we end up doing it again next year we will know what we can improve. We've provided this form for that purpose. You can also email us at any time at <a href="mailto:vidya@vidyagaemawards.com">vidya@vidyagaemawards.com</a>.</p>
		<p>All of the fields below are optional, and you don't have to sign in to submit.</p>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="row" style='margin-top: 20px;'>
	<div class="span12">
		<form class="form-stacked" method="POST">
			
			<fieldset>
			<legend>These first two questions use the modern video game review scale.</legend>
			
			<div class="row">
        <div class="span6">
          <div class="clearfix">
            <label for="general">In general, what did you think of the whole Vidya Gaem Awards?</label>
            <div class="input">
              <select name="general" id="general" class="span3">
                <option value="0">--</option>
                <option value="5" style="background-color: #63BE7B;">10/10, definitely worth the weight</option>
                <option value="4" style="background-color: #B1D580;">9/10, it was good, but not brilliant</option>
                <option value="3" style="background-color: #FFEB84;">8/10, wasn't really good or bad</option>
                <option value="2" style="background-color: #FBAA77;">7/10, pretty bad</option>
                <option value="1" style="background-color: #F8696B;">6/10, kill yourselves</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="span6">
			
          <div class="clearfix">
            <label for="ceremony">What did you think of the award ceremony?</label>
            <div class="input">
              <select name="ceremony" id="ceremony" class="span3">
                <option value="0">--</option>
                <option value="5" style="background-color: #63BE7B;">10/10, best shit ever</option>
                <option value="4" style="background-color: #B1D580;">9/10, not perfect but still good</option>
                <option value="3" style="background-color: #FFEB84;">8/10, pretty average</option>
                <option value="2" style="background-color: #FBAA77;">7/10, not worth watching</option>
                <option value="1" style="background-color: #F8696B;">6/10, kill yourselves</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>
        
        </div>
      </div>
      
			</fieldset>
			
			<fieldset style="margin-top: 20px;">
			<legend>Textual feedback</legend>			

			<div class="clearfix">
				<label for="best">What was the best thing about the award ceremony?</label>
				<div class="input">
					<input id="best" name="best" type="text" class="span8" />
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="clearfix">
				<label for="worst">What was the worst thing about the award ceremony?</label>
				<div class="input">
					<input id="worst" name="worst" type="text" class="span8" />
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="clearfix">
				<label for="comments">Use this box to provide comments on anything related to the Vidya Gaem Awards, good or bad.</label>
				<div class="input">
					<textarea id="comments" name="comments" class="span8" rows="12"></textarea>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="clearfix">
				<label for="questions">Do you have any questions for the /v/GA team? We will try and answer these questions in an FAQ.</label>
				<div class="input">
					<textarea id="questions" name="questions" class="span8" rows="6"></textarea>
				</div>
			</div>
			</fieldset>
			
			<fieldset style="margin-top: 20px;">
        <legend>Contact details</legend>
        <div class="clearfix">
          <label for="email">You can choose to enter your email address here, which will allow us to contact you if we have any questions about your feedback.<br>This is completely optional, so feel free to leave it blank.</label>
          <div class="input">
            <input id="email" name="email" type="text" class="span8" placeholder="Email address (optional)" maxlength="255" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="clearfix">
          <div class="input">
            <input type="submit" class="btn btn-large btn-primary" value="Submit feedback">
          </div>
        </div>
			</fieldset>
		</form>
	</div>
</div>
</if:false>